{"tid":696534,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"好悶呀","createTime":"2018-06-10T07:38:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-10T08:16:52.000Z","uid":105665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"265fdea19e86dec5dfe794869b064472d6af9d50","tid":696534,"uid":105665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T07:38:12.000Z","msg":"冇人同我出街冇人約 買埋一堆衫又唔知著比邊個睇 除左返工真係冇野好做 <br />\n骨子裡我係好怕悶又有過度活躍既人<br />\n偏偏冇人同自己癲真係好辛苦<br />\n個個天口慶小小寧願係屋企灘屍都唔願同我冷街<br />\n今日有咩地方好去<br />\n都知唔會有巴打絲打想我一齊街架啦<br />\n覺得就算得自己都好 都要出下去<br />\n再屈係屋企我會死的<br />\n利申 樣衰柒頭 要拎去人道毀滅果種"},{"pid":"b3d0a0338b25ac909c4208391cd8313dbaf8ebd9","tid":696534,"uid":50744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T07:39:16.000Z","msg":"毒撚是孤獨的狼<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ef15059591242caf690ce1dd2c41eec50a04005","tid":696534,"uid":105665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b3d0a0338b25ac909c4208391cd8313dbaf8ebd9","tid":696534,"uid":50744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T07:39:16.000Z","msg":"毒撚是孤獨的狼<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T07:50:09.000Z","msg":"好悶"},{"pid":"8535d9f0b4e46e30cecdb97fba11a80b3fee65f2","tid":696534,"uid":105665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T08:16:52.000Z","msg":"自己行葵廣.."}]}